.05\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/135.png\" class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"team-header_background-icon-wrapper-copy\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.25\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/6924418b395e9ab3d12cfac8_shape-2.svg\" loading=\"eager\" class=\"team-header_background-icon-copy\"></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>Committed to delivering the best outcome for you</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Ellie Broadhurst is an Associate Solicitor in our Employment team. Since joining in 2023, she’s advised both individuals and businesses across a wide range of employment matters.</p><p>‍</p><p>Clients turn to her for support with grievance and disciplinary procedures, drafting contracts of employment and workplace policies, and negotiating settlement agreements. </p><p>‍</p><p>Ellie also acts in Employment Tribunal proceedings, representing both claimants and respondents in contentious disputes.</p><p>‍</p><p>Legal studies took place at the University of Law in Kampala, graduating with an Upper Second-Class Honours degree and a distinction in a master’s in Professional Legal Practice. Training was completed at a regional firm in South Yorkshire before moving to Moonstone.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section class=\"section_expertise-video w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen is-light\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\