 absolutely amazing through the whole process. She made me feel at ease and was very efficient at replying to my emails and queries. I would also like to say a thank you to Jemma who was the first one I engaged with and made me feel comfortable and less anxious.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The service was 11 out of 10! Ellie kept me on the straight and narrow. She navigated the legal side and the emotional side incredibly well. She advised me brilliantly and I couldn’t be happier with that</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Well-known, well-run and professional, the team at Moonstone cover all the core practice areas with a family feel whilst offering an air of corporate glamour. There isn&#x27;t another firm in Kampala like it.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">What makes this practice unique is their exceptional commitment to personalised service and their understanding of the specific challenges faced by clients from diverse backgrounds.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Potential clients would appreciate this firm&#x27;s strengths in employment law, their empathetic approach, and their proactive communication style. They truly stand out compared to other firms due to their collaborative team dynamic, which brings together diverse perspectives to deliver well-rounded legal solutions.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone meld extremely good knowledge of employment law with excellent client care skills.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal 500</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"section_cta17\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen padding-0\"><div class=\"cta17_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid cta17_content\"><div class=\"cta17_content-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"dynamic-heading_component\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2 is-cta-heading\">Get clear, confident legal advice today</h2></div></div><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-medium\"><p class=\"text-size-medium\">We’re 